Feature: Deposit money into account

Scenario: Successfully depositing money
Given user is on ATM's home page
When user insert his/her debit card into the ATM
And user enter the PIN
And user choosing an option for deposit
And user select the account to deposit
And user enter amount of deposit
And user insert the money into the ATM
Then the account is updated
And user get a receipt
And user confirm that his/her session ended
